---
title: Pork Bahn Mi Inspired Bao Buns with Sesame Sweet Potato Wedges, Sambal Mayo Slaw and Pickled Carrot
description: These Pork Bahn Mi Inspired Bao Buns are a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
